Description: NextPVR media player client (X11, bundled libmpv)
 yauiclient is a 10-foot-UI media player client for NextPVR. This flavour
 targets X11 sessions and bundles its own libmpv 0.41 runtime plus FFmpeg 8
 codec libraries in /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/, isolated from the system mpv
 install. VVC, AV1, HEVC and AVC are all supported on Intel and AMD GPUs
 through VAAPI.
 .
 This package installs to /usr/bin/yauiclient and conflicts with the other
 yauiclient flavours; only one can be installed at a time.

