Description: NextPVR media player client (Wayland, bundled libmpv)
 yauiclient is a 10-foot-UI media player client for NextPVR. This flavour
 targets Wayland sessions (Mutter, KWin, wlroots-based compositors) and
 bundles its own libmpv 0.41 runtime plus FFmpeg 8 codec libraries in
 /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/, isolated from the system mpv install. VVC, AV1,
 HEVC and AVC are all supported on Intel and AMD GPUs through VAAPI.
 .
 This package installs to /usr/bin/yauiclient and conflicts with the other
 yauiclient flavours; only one can be installed at a time.

